! ABSTRACT: 
! 
!	THIS MODULE DEFINES SYMBOLS FOR THE FAL CONTROL BLOCKS WHICH ARE 
!	INVOKED BY THE $FALWRKDEF AND $FALSTBDEF MACROS. 
! 
